---
import SAGPLayout from "../../../../layouts/SAGPLayout.astro";
---

<SAGPLayout title="Distinguished Lectureship Archive | SAGP">

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="kicker">Lectureship Archive</div>
    <h1>Honoring distinguished scholarship.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      The Distinguished Lectureship archive records scholars honored by SAGP for
      substantial contributions to Ancient Greek philosophy.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Recent lectures</h2>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h3>2025 · André Laks</h3>
      <p>“The kouros’ descent. A methodical reading of Parmenides’ route of search?”</p>
      <p><a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/events/distinguished-lectureship/2025/`}>View lecture</a></p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h3>2024 · Geoffrey Lloyd</h3>
      <p>“What is the Use of Ancient Philosophy?”</p>
      <p><a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/events/distinguished-lectureship/2024/`}>View lecture</a></p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h3>2023 · Tony Long</h3>
      <p>“The Stoic Zeus and the Values of Nature”</p>
      <p><a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/events/distinguished-lectureship/2023/`}>View lecture</a></p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h3>2022 · Dorothea Frede</h3>
      <p>“Aristotle’s ‘Political Architect’ and the City of His Prayers”</p>
      <p><a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/events/distinguished-lectureship/2022/`}>View lecture</a></p>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h3>2021 · David Sedley</h3>
      <p>“Divine Anonymity”</p>
      <p><a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/events/distinguished-lectureship/2021/`}>View lecture</a></p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section two-col">
  <div><h2>A record of recognition</h2></div>
  <div>
    <p>
      The archive preserves a growing record of scholars whose work has shaped
      the study of Ancient Greek philosophy and whose contributions have been
      recognized by the Society.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

</SAGPLayout>
